# Build-context hygiene for the repo-root-context image builds (services/ledger
# and services/witness both build with the monorepo root as the Docker context
# so their `replace => ../../libs` resolves). The images COPY only libs/ +
# services/<svc>/ source, but keep local-only artifacts — and CRITICALLY any
# secrets — out of the build context regardless of what a COPY might widen to.
.git
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/*.egg-info
.run
**/.run

# Secrets — never enter an image build context.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/age-key.txt
**/keys.txt
